  <brief_title>Comparison of Radiofrequency Ablation and Cryotherapy for the Treatment of Barrett's Esophagus With High-Grade Dysplasia and/or Early Adenocarcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Trial Comparing Radiofrequency Ablation (Barrx™) and Cryotherapy (TruFreeze™) for the Treatment of Barrett's Esophagus With High-Grade Dysplasia and/or Early Adenocarcinoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
