  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The two treatment modalities under investigation are clinically equivalent (non-inferior) to
      each other for the endoscopic treatment of Barrett's esophagus with HGD and/or early
      esophageal adenocarcinoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
